[CRITICAL JSON RULES]
- DO NOT use words like "Stimulus:" or "Question:" inside the "soal" field. The "soal" field must ONLY contain the actual question sentence.
- STRICTLY PROHIBITED to create questions that highly depend on Images/Tables/Graphs. NEVER use phrases like "Based on the image above...", or "Look at the following table...". Every question MUST be answerable without visual aids!
- Even if there are image references in the Context, ignore them and create independent theoretical questions.
